PRESS DIGEST - Saudi Arabia - Jan 19 . These are some of the leading stories in the Saudi Arabian press on Sunday . Reuters has not verified these stories and does not vouch for their accuracy . ARAB NEWS - The Islamic Development Bank undertakes a study to examine proposals for setting up shipping links between Islamic states . - Sheep prices rise in Saudi Arabia as Haj season approaches . Around two million Moslems perform pilgrimage at the two holy shrines in Mecca and Medina . - Saudi Arabian Airlines to resume flights to Beirut from February . AL - RIYADH - Three technology colleges to be constructed in Saudi Arabia at a cost of 150 million riyals . AL - YAUM - Saudi committee donates around three million riyals to needy people in the Eastern province of Saudi Arabia . 
